\fs22 \cf0 \ulnone \
\pard\tx560\tx1120\tx1680\tx2240\tx2800\tx3360\tx3920\tx4480\tx5040\tx5600\tx6160\tx6720\qj
\cf0 LaTeXiT is a little utility designed to quickly typeset LaTeX equations and drag'n drop them into other applications.\
\
