FAQ (Frequently asked questions)\

\fs22 \ulnone \
(Q): where can I get pdflatex, dvipdf and ghostscript ?\
(A): please see the section "Install Latex" of this document.\
\
(Q): My equation is cut and does not display completely .\
(A): See the "Known issues" section below.\
\
(Q): Which export format should I prefer ?\
(A): PDF is usually the best choice, since it is a "vectorial" format : the image can be resized without loss of quality.\
\
(Q): changes to the preamble seems not take effect unless I quit and restart the application.\
(A): Any modification to the default preamble does not affect currently open windows, since their would be the risk to overwrite some modifications the user has made in them. However, you do not have to restart the application; just open a new document like in any application (\uc0\u8984 N).\
