\fs22 \cf0 \ulnone (Q): LinkBack does not work when I use the LaTeXiT's service.\
(A): See section "Known issues" for more details. To solve this problem, try to disable the baseline alignment of the equation in the LaTeXiT's service preferences.\
\
(Q): The white background of preview pane/text areas is not handy when using white text.\
(A): You can open the color panel and drop a color on these areas.\
\
(Q): I don't understand the "encapsulation" palette.\
(R): This palette fills a very particular need. Usually, it is useless to drag'n drop an equation (as an image) towards an application that cannot display images. However, if this application is a LaTeX text editor, it may be relevant to drag'n drop some text related to the equation : its source code, a \\ref\{\} with its title.... So, this is customizable in the palette, and will work for drag'n drop from the library.\
\
